WIMPY

Use the "wimpy" command to automatically wimp out of a fight.

^c< 10P 10M > wimpy 5^n

will make your character automatically ^Wflee^n a fight if he/she has less
than 6 physical points.

^c< 10P 10M > wimpy 0^n

turns off wimpy mode.

^c< 10P 10M > wimpy^n

shows you your current wimpy status.

^WSee also: TOGGLE, FLEE^n

